        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Dice your <strong>cucumber</strong> finely</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Cut half the cucumber into rounds and leave plain!</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
