    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped shallot</strong> and <strong>diced cucumber </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>cider vinegar </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>pickles</strong></p>",
