      "instruction": "<p>Cut a slit into the top of your<strong> hot dog bun[s]</strong></p><p>Once the chips are nearly done, add the <strong>cut</strong> <strong>hot dog bun[s]</strong> to a separate baking tray, cut side up, and put the tray in the oven for 2-3 min or until warmed through</p>",
